  "_meta": {
    "format_version": 1,
    "description": "Sector and geographic breakdowns for each ETF in the GPCP portfolio. Used by the Pro > Sector / Geo Exposure sub-tab. These numbers are AUTO-SCRAPED on the 15th of each month by monthly_compositions_update.py, which downloads each fund's official month-end factsheet PDF (Amundi/BNP via fundinfo, discovered through justETF) and parses the sector + country tables. IBEX has no monthly factsheet on fundinfo, so its sector data falls back to yfinance (geo stays manual = Spain 100%). The dashboard then weights each ETF by its current portfolio value automatically. last_auto_refresh / last_auto_refresh_source / source_pdf record provenance. To force a refresh now: .venv/bin/python monthly_compositions_update.py",
    "source": "Official issuer factsheets (Amundi, BNP Paribas) via api.fundinfo.com; IBEX sector via yfinance",
    "monthly_refresh_day": 15
  }
